### ============================================
### TEST NEW APIs - BANNERS & GENDER FILTER
### ============================================

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### BANNER APIs - PUBLIC
### ============================================

### 1. Lấy tất cả banners active
GET {{baseUrl}}/banners
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Lấy banners theo position (hero)
GET {{baseUrl}}/banners?position=hero
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Lấy banners theo position (sidebar)
GET {{baseUrl}}/banners?position=sidebar
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Lấy chi tiết banner theo ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/banners/1
Content-Type: application/json

### ============================================
### BANNER APIs - ADMIN
### ============================================

### 5. Lấy tất cả banners (bao gồm inactive) - Admin
GET {{baseUrl}}/banners/admin/all
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6. Tạo banner mới - Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/banners/admin
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "title": "Summer Sale 2024",
  "subtitle": "Giảm giá mùa hè",
  "description": "Giảm giá lên đến 70% cho tất cả sản phẩm mùa hè",
  "image_url": "/images/banners/summer-sale.jpg",
  "mobile_image_url": "/images/banners/summer-sale-mobile.jpg",
  "link_url": "/shop-default?season=summer&is_sale=true",
  "button_text": "Mua ngay",
  "position": "hero",
  "display_order": 1,
  "is_active": true
}

### 7. Cập nhật banner - Admin
PUT {{baseUrl}}/banners/admin/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "title": "Summer Collection 2024 - Updated",
  "is_active": true,
  "display_order": 2
}

### 8. Toggle trạng thái banner - Admin
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/banners/admin/1/toggle-status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 9. Xóa banner - Admin
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/banners/admin/5
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### PRODUCT APIs - FILTER BY GENDER & SEASON
### ============================================

### 10. Lấy sản phẩm nam (male)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?gender=male&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

### 11. Lấy sản phẩm nữ (female)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?gender=female&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

### 12. Lấy sản phẩm unisex
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?gender=unisex&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

### 13. Lấy sản phẩm mùa hè (summer)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?season=summer&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

### 14. Lấy sản phẩm mùa đông (winter)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?season=winter&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

### 15. Kết hợp filter gender + season
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?gender=female&season=summer&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

### 16. Filter nam + giá + sale
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?gender=male&min_price=100000&max_price=500000&is_sale=true
Content-Type: application/json

### ============================================
### PRODUCT ADMIN APIs - WITH GENDER & SEASON
### ============================================

### 17. Tạo sản phẩm mới với gender & season - Admin
