### 20. Lấy sản phẩm bestseller theo gender
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/bestseller?gender=male&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

### 21. Lấy sản phẩm mới theo gender
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/new?gender=female&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

